            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="191114917">
            航班在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13063.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="汕头" target="_blank">汕头</a>经停，1点才到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>，从美兰到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>提前的动车买的是1点28的，肯定赶不上了，打电话<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64941.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="成功" target="_blank">成功</a>退票，扣了20％手续费。终于到啦~
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278439162" data-seq="278439163" data-pid="278439162" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="6003480">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8165970/278439162.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CD/AF/wKgBEFpKDv-ANZ4rAAivoeJqmjQ56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CD/AF/wKgBEFpKDv-ANZ4rAAivoeJqmjQ56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278439162" alt="" />
        </a>
