            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="191376644">
            重新在机场买票坐动车去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>，机场往返<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>的动车还是很多的。到达<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>时打了个飞的直接去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196328.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚湾" target="_blank">三亚湾</a>酒店。<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>的第一天住的是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196328.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚湾" target="_blank">三亚湾</a>青艺术雅筑旅馆，特点在于店内装修和涂鸦，的确旅游文艺气息，特别喜欢一楼的布置，秋千和摇椅，房间设备也有其风格。不好之处在于硬件，房子在街边，晚上很吵，房间不透气，有些许味道。旅馆离<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196328.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚湾" target="_blank">三亚湾</a>步行大概10分钟吧，还是很方便的。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278440076" data-seq="278440079" data-pid="278440076" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="15730620">
