            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278440851" data-seq="278440855" data-pid="278440851" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="10230">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8165970/278440851.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:850px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CE/8A/wKgBEFpKEF6AYamjAAVKTBeD_mo43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CE/8A/wKgBEFpKEF6AYamjAAVKTBeD_mo43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278440851" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/10230.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="10230" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>三亚湾椰梦长廊
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278491837">
            晚上在椰梦长廊附近的餐厅吃的，具体名字忘记了，好像是一块豆腐？<br />
本来以为外婆牙口不好，吃这个会比较习惯，结果菜色真的不敢恭维。<br />
除了豆腐味道还可以之外，其他的真的不咋滴。<br />
后悔没去吃椰子鸡了，对了，我家老人挑食，虽然我不想这么说，哈哈哈。<br />
太甜的吃不惯，喜欢吃辣，不吃蛋糕，等等。
        </p>
