                <a href="/poi/8325614.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="8325614" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="hotel"></i>初见时光一线海景公寓
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278444652">
            悠闲的吃过午饭，便准备开始下午的行程。<br />
我本<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/143300.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="来安" target="_blank">来安</a>排的是打车去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16020.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="亚龙湾" target="_blank">亚龙湾</a>，看看那边的海，再找个酒店喝下午茶。但是看老人在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196328.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚湾" target="_blank">三亚湾</a>也没有很激动呀，可能对海没有很感冒吧，哈哈。所以哪个海对她来说可能都一样，就不花心力折腾了。<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16020.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="亚龙湾" target="_blank">亚龙湾</a>天堂森林公园的话，临时赶过去可能也来不及逛完，在网上查到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16020.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="亚龙湾" target="_blank">亚龙湾</a>附近有个玫瑰谷，问老人家愿不愿意去看看花草，马上就答应了啊喂~<br />
这个景点在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>的跟团游线路中一般都是附赠的景点<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/36@2x.png" style="width:28px;" /><br />
但是投其所好最重要哦。于是，叫了个滴滴直接奔到玫瑰谷了。<br />
Tips：此趟出行一般都是打的滴滴，很少坐公交。<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>的公交时间安排比较随意，还记得自己第一次去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>的时候，烈日下在一个站台等了半个小时的公交，而且每个站台停停顿顿，老人家容易头晕或者胸闷，所以此行吸取教训，直接飞的。<br />
下面就到了玫瑰谷啦，园子比较大其实，如果真的喜欢花草的话，还挺值得一逛。亮点在千亩玫瑰，我们一行三个人难得自恋拍了不少照片。玫瑰谷适<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/58257.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="合阳" target="_blank">合阳</a>光灿烂的日子来，我们抵达的时候已经五点多了，所以颜色不是那么艳丽，外婆却很是欣喜，对这个地方赞不绝口，果然投其所好是多么重要！各色稀奇古怪的品种，估计也让她大开眼界吧，嘴里也不时念叨着自己家门口种的花花草草，看到好看的品种还想谋个苗子回去栽培，哈哈哈哈。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_191488311" data-seq="191488312" data-pid="191488311" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="7045541">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8165970/191488311.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/98/26/wKgBZ1i21EOABRWOAAiKDqWHPW496.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/98/26/wKgBZ1i21EOABRWOAAiKDqWHPW496.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="191488311" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/7045541.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="7045541" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>亚龙湾国际玫瑰谷
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278448719" data-seq="278448722" data-pid="278448719" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="7045541">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8165970/278448719.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D2/B1/wKgBEFpKFdyAUSKQAA69sOgwpD885.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D2/B1/wKgBEFpKFdyAUSKQAA69sOgwpD885.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278448719" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/7045541.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="7045541" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>亚龙湾国际玫瑰谷
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278448720" data-seq="278448723" data-pid="278448720" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="7045541">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8165970/278448720.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D2/B5/wKgBEFpKFd-AfXGaAAiBe5CDu8I81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D2/B5/wKgBEFpKFd-AfXGaAAiBe5CDu8I81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278448720" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/7045541.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="7045541" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>亚龙湾国际玫瑰谷
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="191488319">
            玫瑰谷回来已经是晚上了，晚饭我跟表妹又屁颠去附近的集市逛了一圈，自己买了些海鲜，在阳台坐着吹风看海，喝茶吃饭，额，自己煮的原因，酱料有点咸了，不过悠闲的居家劲儿还是足的。下图夜晚的凤凰岛。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278522689" data-seq="278522690" data-pid="278522689" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:440px" data-poiid="10230">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8165970/278522689.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:324px;width:440px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FB/27/wKgBEFpKUiqAcOJKAAGJQxT3yhU88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/FB/27/wKgBEFpKUiqAcOJKAAGJQxT3yhU88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278522689" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/10230.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="10230" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>三亚湾椰梦长廊
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278522691">
            ————————————————————————————————————————<br />
囧事一波:&nbsp;因为甚是爱上了这个厨房和露天阳台，打算把我明天早晨最后的机会，想在这边做一顿便捷健康又舒适的早餐。晚上十点外婆睡了，我跟表妹出门准备买点饺子，刚走出第一个分叉路口，我隐约记得直走，表妹握着导航义正言辞指着左边。我觉得既然她都握着导航了，而且又这么确切地记得路，那可能是我错了吧。一路上谈笑风生，结果还真走错了路。原来她导的是两公里开外的另一家分店，10分钟就能解决的事情，我们走了40多分钟，还木有到，快11点的时候，终于抵达另一家，果不其然关门了。于是两个人踩着沉重的步子，空着手吹着凌晨瑟瑟的海风回来了，到家就感冒了一个月。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_191527535" data-seq="191527536" data-pid="191527535" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:400px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8165970/191527535.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:495px;width:400px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B0/2D/wKgBZ1i3AlmAEUpOAAH57GS6u3U50.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B0/2D/wKgBZ1i3AlmAEUpOAAH57GS6u3U50.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="191527535" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278451837">
            大半夜，从<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196328.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚湾" target="_blank">三亚湾</a>海边走到了解放路步行街，哼唧！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_191527537" data-seq="191527538" data-pid="191527537" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8165970/191527537.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B0/2D/wKgBZ1i3AlqAWToUAAj0EJCAIVo40.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B0/2D/wKgBZ1i3AlqAWToUAAj0EJCAIVo40.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="191527537" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div data-seq="278452682" data-index="5" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <img src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D4/AF/wKgBEFpKGMuAQKtsAAAI7DiAHek847.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fh%2F150%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" class="no_word _j_anchor" title="第3,4天：南山" alt="第3,4天：南山" />
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="191827073">
            第三天，满血复活前往南山，也是本次旅行的重头戏。<br />
我们家都是信佛的，尤其是老年人，到了日子就要去寺庙烧高香。南山一方面是位置比较偏，另一方面由于我们也想在这多玩玩，所以定了南山景区里的酒店。南山的酒店有两个，南山休闲会馆和南山国宾馆，我们选择了南山休闲会馆。<br />
晨起出门坐巴士直达南山寺路口，打电话给南山休闲会馆就有游览车来接。（房间是提前半个月电话预定的）这里不得不夸下南山休闲会馆，房间硬件一般，但是在南山游览的话，订间景区酒店真的很方便，从景区门口到酒店大堂到南山路口都是车接车送，可免2人的景区门票。住在南山酒店里面，早晚会有一系列的礼佛活动，一晚房费八百多，但是算算还是划得来的。<br />
另老年人进南山可以免门票，具体是75岁以上还是80岁以上可以免，这里记不清了，有需要可以自己百度查一下。所以我们此行三人进南山，等于不需要出门票的费用了，简直不能太开心~<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/5@2x.png" style="width:28px;" /><br />
简单发一下酒店的照片，我们订的是潮音海景房，在南山的半山腰上，房间可以直接看到观音。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278456959" data-seq="278456960" data-pid="278456959" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="17455">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8165970/278456959.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:639px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D7/37/wKgBEFpKHPeAShABAAW5gdUvlPw17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D7/37/wKgBEFpKHPeAShABAAW5gdUvlPw17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278456959" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/17455.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="17455" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="hotel"></i>南山休闲会馆
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278455009" data-seq="278455021" data-pid="278455009" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="17455">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8165970/278455009.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D5/EF/wKgBEFpKGo2ADWLdAAXbu2cq0-Y62.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D5/EF/wKgBEFpKGo2ADWLdAAXbu2cq0-Y62.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278455009" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/17455.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="17455" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="hotel"></i>南山休闲会馆
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
    
